sub_title: entrepreneur + OJMAR business manager The Netherlands & Flanders (Belgium)
summary:
I provide (the small) entrepreneur with the option of employing an account manager, without the costs of a full-time employee. Available full-time - part-time.
So; expansion of sales where and when it is needed.

Interim, Freelance or Part-time ... whatever we call it ... Flexibility is perhaps my most important characteristic! Complete self-support and with car, laptop, telephone and agenda.

A flexible contract based on an average number of hours that can be adjusted at any time in the process.

You point the fruits ... and I pick them for you!
